title: BRIEF-NetApp Q4 GAAP Earnings Per Share $0.99
text:
May 23 (Reuters) - NetApp Inc:
* NETAPP REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FISCAL YEAR 2018 RESULTS
* Q4 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.99 * Q4 REVENUE $1.64 BILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $1.6 BILLION
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.01 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* QTRLY NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE OF $1.05
* SEES Q1 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.76 TO $0.82 * SEES Q1 NET REVENUES IN THE RANGE OF $1.365 BILLION TO $1.465 BILLION
* SEES Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.53 TO $0.59 * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.78, REVENUE VIEW $1.42 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
